nodes.text: The A-1 Deluxe Floater was a capsule-shaped landspeeder featuring a pod-like cockpit. During the secret mission to Tatooine in 0 BBY, one such vehicle was parked outside Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina in Mos Eisley, Tatooine, as Luke Skywalker and Obi-Wan Kenobi were about to enter the premises.
